hadiths[96]{hadithnumber,text}:
3792,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( umuman ) yun qism khaya kartey they : qism us zaat ki jo dilon ko pherney wali hai ! baat aisey nahin."
3793,"Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki qism , jo aap umuman uthaya kartey they, ye thi : mujhey qism hai us zaat ki jo dilon ko pherney wali hai ! maamla aisey nahin."
3794,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Allah Taala ney jannat aur jahannam ko paida farmaya to Hazrat Jibril alehissalam ko jannat ki taraf bheja aur farmaya : jaao, jannat aur is mein jannatiyon key liye banai hui chizon ko dekho. unhoney ja kar dekha, phir wapis aaye to kehney lagey : teri izzat ki qism ! jo shakhs bhi jannat key barey mein sunega, zarur is mein dakhil hoga. Allah Taala ney hukm diya to jannat ko sakhtiyon aur tabaa aur nagawar guzarney wali chizon sey gher diya gaya. Allah Taala ney farmaya : ab phir jaao aur dekho ke mainey jannat mein apney bandon key liye kya kuch banaya hai. unhoney ja kar dekha to jannat key ird-gird sakhtiyon aur mushkilat ki baad lagi hui thi. wo aa kar kehney lagey : teri izzat ki qasam! mujhey khatra hai ke koi shakhs bhi is mein dakhil nahin ho (sakey) ga. Allah Taala ney farmaya : jaao aag ( jahannam ) ko dekho aur jo kuch mainey ehal jahannam key liye tayyar kar rakha hai. unhoney ja kar dekha to aag key sholay eik dusrey sey takra rahey they. wo wapis aa kar kehney lagey : teri izzat ki qasam! koi is mein dakhil nahin hoga. Allah Taala ney hukm diya to uskey ird-gird tabiat ki marghoob chizon ki baad laga di gaee. farmaya : ab jakar dekho. unhoney dekha to uskey ird-gird khushnuma chizon ki baadh lag chuki thi. wo wapis aa kar kehney lagey : teri izzat ki qism ! mujhey khatra hai ke koi shakhs us sey nahin bach sakega . zarur dakhil ho jaeyga."
3795,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs qism khana chahey wo Allah Taala key siwa kisi ki qism na khaye. Quraish apney aabaa-w ijdaad ki qasmen khaya kartey they, lihaza aap ney farmaya : apney aabaa-w ijdaad ki qasmen na khaya karo."
3796,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba Allah Taala tumhen mana farmata hai ke tum apney aabaa-w ijdaad ki qasmen khaao.
3797,"Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik dafa kehtey suna : merey baap ki qasam! merey baap ki qasam! aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala tumhen aabaa-w ijdaad key naam ki qasmen khaney sey mana farmata hai. (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya :) Allah ki qism ! uskey baad mainey kabhi bhi aisi qism nahin khai. na apney taur par, na kisi ki naqal kartey huye."
3798,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala tumhen aaba-w ijdaad ki qism khaney sey mana farmata hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! uskey baad mainey kabhi aisi qism nahin khai. na apney taur par, na kisi sey naqal kartey huye."
3799,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba Allah Taala tumhen aabaa-w ijdaad ki qasmen khaney sey rokta hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mainey uskey baad kabhi aabaa-w ijdaad ki qism nahin khai. na apney taur par , na kisi sey naqal kartey huye."
3800,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : na tum aaba-w ijdaad ki qism khao, na maaon ki aur na buton ki, balke sirf Allah ki qism khao aur sirf usi waqt khao jab tum sachchey ho."
3801,"Hazrat Sabit bin Zahhak (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs jhoota honey key bawajud amadan Islam key ilawa kisi aur Deen ki qism khaye to wo aisey hi hoga jaisey us ney kaha. aur jis shakhs ney kisi chiz sey khudkushi kar li, Allah Taala jahannam ki aag mein usey usi chiz key sath azab deta rahega."
3802,"Hazrat Sabit bin Zuhhak (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney jhoota honey key bawajud kisi aur Deen ki qism khai to wo isi tarah hai jis tarah us ney kaha. aur jo shakhs apney aap ko kisi chiz sey qatl kar daley, usey aakhirat mein usi chiz key sath azab diya jaeyga."
3803,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kahe : (agar mainey falan kaam kiya ho to) main Islam sey laataalluq hun. agar wo jhoota hai to phir wo haqiqat mein Islam sey laataalluq hai. aur agar wo sachcha hai to phir bhi wo sahih salim Islam ki taraf nahin loteyga.
3804,"Juhaina qabiley ki eik aurat Hazrat Qutaila (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi shakhs Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kaha : tum bhi shirk kartey ho aur ghairullah ko mabood banatey ho kyonkey tum kehtey ho : jo Allah Taala chahey aur aap chahen. aur tum Kaba ki qism khatey ho. to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon ko hukm diya ke jab wo qism khaney lagen to kahin : Kaba ke Rab ki qism ! aur kahin jo Allah Taala chahey, phir aap chahen."
3805,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum apney aabaa-w-ijdaad aur buton ki qasmen na khao.
3806,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs laat ki qism khaye, wo kahe : (لا الہ الا اللہ), ''(Allah taala key siwa koi mabood nahin)'' aur jo shakhs apney sathi sey kahe : aao main tum sey jua khelon to usey sadqa karna chahiye."
3807,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik dafa kisi mamley mein behes kar rahey they. mera daure-jahiliyat abhi taza tha. main laat aur uzzaa ki qism kha betha to mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba kehney lagey : tu ney buri baat kahi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas jaao aur aap ko ye baat batao. hum to samajhtey hain ke tu ney kalima kufr kaha hai. mein aap ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap ko puri baat batai. aap ney mujhey farmaya : teen dafa keh : Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. wo yaktaa hai. koi us ka sajhi nahin. aur teen dafa shetan sey (bachney key liye) Allah Taala ki panah mang aur teen dafa apney baain taraf thook dey aur dobara aisi baat na kehna."
3808,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Laat aur Uzzaa ki qism kha betha to mujhey merey sathi kehney lagey : tu ney bahut bura kalima kaha aur bahut qabeeh baat ki hai. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur ye baat aap sey zikr ki. aap ney farmaya : teen dafa keh : Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. wo akela hai. us ka koi shareek nahin. usi key liye badshahi hai. usi key liye tareef hai. aur wo har chiz par qadir hai. aur teen dafa apney baain janib thook dey aur shetan sey bachao key liye Allah ki panah talab kar aur phir dobara aisi baat na karna."
3809,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein saat chizon ka hukm diya : janaazon key sath jana, mareez ki bimar pursi karna, chhinkney waley ko dua dena, dawat deney waley ki dawat qubul karna, mazloom ki madad karna, qism khaney waley ki qism ko pura karna aur salam ka jawab dena."
3810,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main is zamin ki jis chiz par bhi qism kha lun, phir uskey ilawa kisi aur chiz ko behtar dekhun to main wo behtar kaam karunga."
3811,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main kuchh Ash-ari afrad key sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. hum aap sey (jihad key silsiley mein) sawariyan maangney aaye they. aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main tumhein sawariyan nahin dunga aur na merey paas sawariyan hain. phir hum thehrey rahey jitni der Allah ney chaha ke (baad mein) aap key paas kuchh oont laye gaey. aap ney hamein teen oont deney ka hukm diya. jab hum oont ley kar chal padey to hamney eik dusrey sey kaha : Allah Taala hamarey liye in oonton mein barkat nahin farmaeyga kyonkey jab hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sawariyan maangney aaye they to aap ney qism khai thi ke main tumhen sawariyan nahin dunga. (ab shayad aap qism bhool gaey hain, ye soch kar) hum dobara Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur aap sey sari baat zikr ki. aap ney farmaya : mainey tumhen sawariyan nahin dein balke Allah Taala ney di hain. Allah ki qism ! agar main kisi chiz par qism kha lun, phir main uski bajaey koi aur chiz behtar samjhoon to main qism ka kaffara dey deta hun aur behtar kaam kar leta hun."
3812,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi chiz par qism khaye , phir uski bajaey koi aur chiz behtar samjhey to apni qism ka kaffara dey dey aur behtar kaam kar ley."
3813,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey hain, aap ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi kisi kaam ki qism khaye, phir koi aur kaam us sey behtar samjhey to usey chahiye ke wo apni qism ka kaffara dey aur jisey wo behtar samajh raha hai us kaam ko amal mein laye."
3814,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( mujh sey) farmaya : jab to kisi kaam ki qism khaye (aur phir koi aur kaam behtar samjhey ) to ( pehley) apni qism ka kaffara dey dey aur behtar kaam kar ley.
3815,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to kisi kaam ki qism kha ley, phir to koi aur kaam ziyada achcha samjhey to apni qism ka kaffara de-dey aur jo kaam ziyada achcha hai, wo kar ley."
3816,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi chiz par qism kha ley, phir kisi dusri chiz ko us sey behtar khayal karey to behtar chiz par amal karey aur apni qism ka kaffara de-dey."
3817,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs koi kaam karney ki qism khaye, phir kisi aur kaam ko us sey behtar khayal karey to apni qism ko chhod dey aur wo kaam karey jo behtar ho, albatta kaffara dey dey."
3818,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi kaam ki qism kha ley, phir kisi dusrey kaam ko us sey behtar samjhey to behtar kaam kar ley aur apni qism chhod dey."
3819,"Hazrat Abul-Ehwas apney walid mohtaram sey riwayat kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney chacha zaad bhai key paas jata hun aur us sey kuch maangta hun to wo mujhey nahin deta aur mujh sey sila rehmi nahin karta , phir kabhi wo mera mohtaj ho jata hai aur merey paas aa kar mujh sey maangta hai jabkey main qism kha chuka hun ke main usey nahin dunga aur us sey sila rehmi nahin karunga. farmaiye, main kya karun? aap ney mujhey hukm diya ke main wo kaam karun jo behtar hai (yani us sey sila rehmi karun ) aur apni qism ka kaffara de-dun."
3820,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jab to kisi kaam ki qism kha ley, phir koi aur kaam us sey behtar samjhey to behtar kaam kar ley aur apni qism ka kaffara dey dey."
3821,"Hazrat abu-Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( mujh sey) farmaya : jab to kisi kaam ko karney ki qism kha ley, phir to uski bajaey koi aur kaam us sey behtar samjhey to jo kaam behtar hai wo kar ley aur apni qism ka kaffara ada kar dey."
3822,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jab to koi kaam karney ki qism kha ley, phir to koi aur kaam us sey behtar samjhey to jo behtar hai usey amal mein ley aa aur apni qism ka kaffara dey dey."
3823,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo chiz milkiyat mein nahin, is mein na nazar maana ja sakti hai, na qism khai ja sakti hai. aur (usi tarah Allah Taala ki) nafarmani aur qata-rehmi ki nazar aur qism bhi moatabar nahin."
3824,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs qism khatey waqt inshaAllah keh dey, wo chahey to qism ko pura karey aur chahey to chhod dey. usey koi gunah nahin hoga."
3825,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba aamal ka madaar niiyaton par hai. aur har shakhs ko wohi milega jiski us ney niyat ki, chunanche jis shakhs ki ( niyat ) hijrat ( kartey waqt ) Allah aur uskey Rasool (ki raza mandi aur hukm ki taameel ) key liye hogi to uski hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool key liye hi samjhi jaeygi lekin jis shakhs ki hijrat (ka maqsud ) duniya ka husool aur kisi aurat sey nikah waghera tha to uski hijrat unhi chizon key liye samjhi jaeygi jo us ka maqsud thin."
3826,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (apni eik biwi) Hazrat Zainab bint Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan ziyada der thehertey they kyonkey aap wahan sey shehad peetey they. mainey aur Hafsa ney aapas mein ittifaq kya ke hum mein sey jis key paas Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laeyn to wo kahey: bilashuba mein aap sey maghafir ki bo mehsus kar rahi hun. aap ney maghafir ( gond ) khai hai? aap hum mein sey kisi eik key yahan tashrif laye to usney ye lafz keh diye. aap ney farmaya : nahin, balke mainey to Zainab bint Jahash key yahan sey shehad piya hai. dobara hergiz nahin piyunga. to phir ye aayaat utren : « { یٰاَیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ لِمَ تُحَرِّمُ maa اَحَلَّ اللّٰہُ لَکَ }  aey Nabi ! aap us chiz ko kyon haram qarar dey rahey hain jisey Allah Taala ney aap key liye halal qarar diya hai? aagey Hazrat Aaisha aur Hafsa sey khitab kartey huye farmaya : { اِنْ تَتُوْبَآ اِلَی اللّٰہِ }  agar tum Allah Taala key huzur ( apni ghalati sey) tauba karo (to tumhen laaiq hai). ( وَ اِذْ اَسَرَّ النَّبِیُّ اِلیٰ بَعْضِ اَزْوَاجِہِ حَدِیْثًا ) jab Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni eik biwi sey raz ki baat kahi padhi. is mein ishara hai aap key farman ki taraf ke padhi. mainey to shehad piya hai, ( aainda nahin piyunga)."
3827,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath aap key kisi ghar mein dakhil huwa to aap ko roti key tukdey aur sirka pesh kiye gaey. aap ney mujhey farmaya : khao sirka behtareen salan hai.
3828,"Hazrat Qais bin abi Gharza (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hamen (tajiron ko) dalaal kaha jata tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas (bazar mein) tashrif laye. hum kharid o farokht kar rahey they. aap ney hamarey naam sey behtar naam hamarey liye muqarrar farmaya. aap ney farmaya : aey tajiron ki jamaat! bechtey waqt (kabhi-kabhi bila qasad) qism aur jhoot sadir ho jatey hain, lihaza tum farokht key sath sath sadqa bhi kya karo."
3829,"Hazrat Qais bin abi Gharza (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum baqee key bazar mein kharid o farokht kya kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye. hamen us waqt Samsar (dalaal) kaha jata tha. aap ney farmaya : usey tajiron ki jamaat! to aap ney hamarey sabiqa naam sey behtar naam rakha. phir farmaya : kharid o farokht kartey waqt (bila qasad) qism aur jhoot sadir ho jatey hain, lihaza sath sath sadqa bhi kya karo."
3830,"Hazrat Qais bin abi Gharza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye jabkey hum bazar mein ( tijarat kar rahey ) they. aap ney farmaya is bazar mein fuzul baaton aur jhoot ki aamezish hoti rehti hai, lihaza sadqa kartey raho."
3831,"Hazrat Qais bin abi Gharza (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Madina Munawra mein ghalley ki kharid o farokht kya kartey they aur apney aap ko samsar kaha kartey they. log bhi hamen yehi kehtey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik din hamarey paas tashrif laye. aap ney hamen hamarey aur logon key rakhey huye naam sey behtareen naam diya. aap ney farmaya : aey tajiron ki jamaat ! tumharey soodon mein (bila qasd (irada) o irada) jhoot aur qasmon ki milawat hoti rehti hai, lihaza tum apney soodon key sath sath sadqey ki bhi milawat kya karo."
3832,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney nazar manney sey mana kya hai aur farmaya : uska koi faeyda nahin, albatta uskey sath bakheel aadmi sey kuch maal nikal aata hai."
3833,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney nazar manney sey mana kya aur farmaya : nazar kisi taqdir ko radd nahin karti, albatta is tareeqey sey kanjus aadmi sey kuch na kuch maal nikala jata hai."
3834,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nazar kisi chiz ko aagey-peechey nahin karti, albatta ye aisi chiz hai jis key sath kanjus aadmi sey kuch na kuch maal nikala jata hai."
3835,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (Allah taala ney farmaya :) nazar insan key liye koi aisi chiz nahin laati jo mainey uskey liye muqaddar na ki ho, albatta iskey zariey sey bakheel shakhs sey kuch maal nikala jata hai."
3836,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nazar na maana karo kyonkey nazar taqdir ko radd nahin kar sakti. uskey sath to bakheel sey kuch maal nikala jata hai.
3837,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala ki kisi itaat ki nazar maaney to usey chahiye ke wo Allah Taala ki itaat karey aur jo shakhs Allah Taala ki kisi nafarmani ki nazar maaney to wo Allah Taala ki nafarmani na kerey.
3838,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs Allah Taala ki itaat ki nazar maaney wo itaat kerey. aur jo shakhs Allah Taala ki nafarmani ki nazar maaney to wo hergiz nafarmani na kerey.
3839,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs Allah Taala ki itaat ki nazar maaney to usey chahiye ke wo Allah Taala ki itaat karey aur jo shakhs Allah Taala ki nafarmani ki nazar maaney to wo uski nafarmani ( bilkul ) na kerey."
3840,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtareen log merey daur key hain, phir jo log unkey baad ayengey aur phir jo unkey baad ayengey aur phir jo unkey baad ayengey. (raawi hadees ney kaha : ) mujhey yad nahin ke aap ney ye lafz do dafa farmaai ya teen dafa. phir aap ney aisey logon ka zikr farmaya jo khayanat kerengey yahan tak ke unkey paas amanat nahin rakhi jaeygi. gawahiyon dengey jabkey un sey gawahi talab nahin ki jaeygi. wo nazrein maanengey magar puri nahin kerengey aur un mein motaapa aam ho jaeyga. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke nasar bin Imran ki kunniyat abu-Jamra hai ( abu-Hamza nahin )."
3841,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jo eik dusrey aadmi ko rassi baandh kar khinch raha tha. aap ney wo rassi pakad kar kaat di. wo kehney laga : mainey ye nazar maana thi.
3842,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jo Kaba ka tawaf kar raha tha. usey eik aur insan uski naak mein nakel dal kar khinch raha tha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney daste-mubarak sey usey kaat diya aur usey hukm diya ke uska haath pakad kar usey chala. is riwayat mein ye lafz bhi aatey hain ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tawaf key doran main eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jisney apna haath kisi dusrey aadmi key sath rassi ya dhaagey waghera key sath baandh rakha tha, chunanche Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney daste-mubarak sey us rassi ko kaat diya aur farmaya : Isey haath pakad kar chala."
3843,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ki nafarmani aur insan ki ghair mamlooka chiz (aisi chiz jiska malik nhai bana ja sakta) mein nazar man'na ghair moatabar hai.
3844,Hazrat Saqib bin Zuhhak (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Deen Islam key ilawa kisi aur Deen ki qism khaye aur ho bhi jhoota to wo isi tarah hoga jis tarah us ney (apney aap ko) kaha. aur jo shakhs duniya mein kisi chiz sey khudkushi kerey. qiyamat key din usey usi chiz key sath azab diya jaeyga. aur kisi shakhs key liye us nazar ko pura karna jaaiz nahi jo us ney apni ghair mamlooka chiz (aisi chiz jiska malik nhai bana ja sakta) key barey mein maana ho.
3845,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke meri behan ney Baitullah tak pedal janey ki nazar maani, phir us ney mujh sey kaha ke main iskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey istifsaar (sawal) karun, chunanche mainey uskey liye Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ye masla puchha to aap ney farmaya : pedal bhi chaley aur sawar bhi ho."
3846,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey apni eik behan key barey mein puchha jisney nazar maana thi ke wo nangey paaun, nangey sar aur pedal jaeygi. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kaho ke sar dhaanpey aur sawar ho jaey aur teen din key rozey rakh ley."
3847,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aurat samandari safar par gaee. us ney nazar maana ke (sahih salaamat wapsi ki surat mein) wo eik maah key rozey rakheygi. lekin wo rozey rakhney sey qabl hi faut ho gaee. uski behan Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur ye soorate-haal aap sey zikr ki to aap ney hukm diya ke to uski taraf sey rozey rakh ley."
3848,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik nazar key barey mein puchha jo un ki walida key zimmey thi lekin wo uski adaaegi sey pehley faut ho gaee thi. aap ney farmaya : tum uski taraf sey ada kar do.
3849,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik nazar key barey mein puchha jo un ki walida key zimmey thi magar wo uski adaegi sey pehley faut ho gaee thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum uski taraf sey ada kar do."
3850,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur kaha : meri walida faut ho gaee hai. uskey zimmey eik nazar thi jisey wo ada nahin kar saki thi. aap ney farmaya : tum uski taraf sey ada kar do."
3851,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain ke unkey zimmey jahiliyat main eik raat aetikaf bethney ki nazar thi. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney unhen (eik raat) aetikaf bethney ka hukm diya.
3852,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key zimmey (daure-jahiliyat mein) eik raat Masjide-Haram mein aetikaf bethney ki nazar thi. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey iskey mutalliq puchha to aap ney unhen aetikaf bethney ka hukm diya."
3853,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney daure-jahiliyat main eik din aetikaf bethney ki nazar maana thi. (musalman honey key baad) unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is barey mein puchha to aap ney unhen aetikaf bethney ka hukm diya.
3854,Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab un ki tauba qubul hui to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney kul maal ko Allah aur uskey Rasool ki marzi key mutabiq sadqa kartey huye us sey lataaluq hona chahta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apna kuchh maal rakh ley. ye terey liye behtar hoga. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke mumkin hai Zohri ney ye hadees Abdullah bin Kaab sey bhi suni ho aur un sey (unkey bhai) Abdur-Rehman bin Kaab key wastey sey bhi. is lambi hadees mein Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki tauba ka zikr hai.
3855,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Kaab sey riwayat hai ke unhoney (apney walid mohtaram) Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna waqia bayan kartey huye suna, jab wo ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey peechhey reh gaey they. unhoney farmaya : jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney betha to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri tauba mein sey ye bhi hai ke main apney maal ko Allah aur uskey Rasool ki raza mandi key liye sadqa kartey huye apney maal sey lataaluq ho jaaun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apna kuchh maal rakh ley. ye terey liye behtar hai. mainey kaha : main apni Khaibar wali jaaidaad rakh leta hun. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
3856,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Kaab bin Malik sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey (apney walid mohtaram) Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna waqia bayan farmatey huye suna, jab wo ghazwa-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey peechhey reh gaey they. unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri tauba mein sey ye bhi hai ke main apna maal Allah aur uskey Rasool key liye sadqa kartey huye us sey lataaluq ho jaaun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apna kuchh maal rakh ley. ye terey liye behtar hoga. mainey kaha : main apna khaibar wala hissa rakh leta hun."
3857,"Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala ney mujhey sach bolney ki wajeh sey najat di hai, isi ke sath meri tauba mein sey ye bhi hai ke main apna sara maal Allah aur uskey Rasool ki raza mandi ki khatir sadqa kartey huye us sey lataaluq ho jaaun. aap ney farmaya : apna kuchh maal rakh ley, ye terey liye behtar hoga. mainey kaha : theek hai. main apna khaibar wala hissa rakh leta hun."
3858,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum ghazwae-Khaibar waley saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they to hamein ghanimat mein sirf maal, gharelu saman aur kapdey waghera hi miley they. banu Zubaib key eik aadmi Hazrat Rifaa bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap ko eik kaalaa ghulam bator tohfa diya. us ka naam Mud'am tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wadi Quraa ki janib chaley jab hum wadi Quraa mein pahunchey to Mud'am Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (ki sawari) ka paalaan waghera utaar raha tha ke eik teer aaya. usey laga aur usey khatam kar diya. log kehney lagey : isey jannat mubarak ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hergiz nahin, us zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! bilashuba wo chadar jo us ney ghazwae-khaibar key din (meri ijazat key baghair) maale-ghanimat sey uthai thi, is par aag ban kar bhadak rahi hai. jab logon ney ye baat suni to koi aadmi eik tasma, koi do tasmey ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunch gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye eik do tasmey bhi aag ka sabab ban saktey hain."
3859,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney qism khatey waqt Insha-Allah keh diya, us ney ikhtiyar hasil kar liya."
3860,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney qism khatey waqt Insha-Allah keh diya us ney qism pura karney sey istisna hasil kar liya.
3861,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney kisi chiz par qism khai aur sath hi Insha-Allah keh diya to usey ikhtiyar hai. chahey to usey pura kerey. chahey pura na karey.
3862,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik dafa Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud alehissalam ney farmaya : main raat ko apni nawwey (90) aurton key paas zarur jaaunga. un mein sey har eik shehsawaar janeygi jo Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad kerega. aap key sathi ney aap sey (bator talqin) kaha : Insha-Allah, lekin aap ney Insha-Allah na kaha, phir aap un sab aurton key paas gaey lekin un mein sey kisi ko bhi hamal na thehra siwaye eik aurat key. us ney bhi naqis bachcha jana. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! agar wo Insha-Allah keh detey to sab bachchey shehsawaar ban kar Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad kartey."
3863,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nazar ka kaffara (wohi hai jo) qism ka kaffara hai.
3864,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gunah wali nazar puri nahin kerni chahiye.
3865,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah ney farmaya : Allah ki nafarmani wali nazar puri nahin kerni chahiye. aisi nazar ka kaffara qism key kaffaarey ki tarah hai.
3866,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki nafarmani wali nazar moatabar nahin aur us ka kaffara qism wala kaffara hai.
3867,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ma'siyat (nafarmani) wali nazar puri na ki jaey (balke us ka kaffara diya jaey) aur us ka kaffara qism wala hai.
3868,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ma'siyat (nafarmani) ki nazar moatabar nahin aur us ka kaffara qism key kaffaarey ki tarah hai. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke kaha gaya hai ke Imam Zohri ney Hazrat Abu-Salma sey ye riwayat nahin suni.
3869,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gunah ki nazar puri nahin kerni chahiye (balke is mein kaffara hai) aur us ka kaffara qism wala hai.
3870,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki nafarmani wali nazar puri na ki jaey (balke us ka kaffara diya jaey) aur aisi nazar ka kaffara qism key kaffaarey jaisa hai. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain : (raawi hadees) Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Arqam matrakul hadees hai. (wallahu-aalam). is hadees mein Yahya bin Abi Kasir key kaee eik shagirdon ney iski mukhalifat ki hai.
3871,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gunah ki nazar moatabar nahin aur us ka kaffara qism key kaffaarey key barabar hai.
3872,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ma'siyat (nafarmani) ki nazar moatabar nahin aur us ka kaffara qism wala kaffara hai.
3873,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghussey mein aa kar maana hui nazar moatabar nahin aur us ka kaffara qism key kaffaarey ki tarah hai. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain : (raawi hadees) Muhammad bin Zuber Zaeef hai, aisa shakhs hujjat nahin hota, wesey bhi is hadees mein is par ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai."
3874,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghussey ki haalat mein nazar moatabar nahin aur us ka kaffara qism ka kaffara hai.
3875,"Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghussey ki haalat mein nazar durust nahin, albatta us ka kaffara qism wala hai. kaha gaya hai ke Zuber ney ye hadees Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey nahin suni."
3876,"ehale-Basra mein sey eik shakhs sey riwayat hai, us ney kaha : main Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) key paas raha. unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : nazar do tarah ki hoti hai : jo nazar Allah Taala ki itaat key barey mein ho, wo to Allah key liye moatabar hogi aur usey pura karna chahiye aur jo nazar Allah Taala ki nafarmani key barey mein ho, wo shetani kaam hai. usey pura nahin kiya jaeyga, albatta us ka kaffara qism key kaffaarey ki tarah hoga."
3877,"eik aadmi ney Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha jisney nazar maan li thi ke main apni qom ki masjid mein namaz padhney nahin jaaunga. Hazrat Imran ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ghussey ki haalat mein nazar moatabar nahin, albatta us ka kaffara qism ka kaffara hai."
3878,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghussey aur nafarmani ki nazar moatabar nahin aur us ka kaffara qism key kaffaarey jaisa hai.
3879,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nafarmani wali nazar durust nahin aur us ka kaffara qism key kaffaarey jaisa hai. alfaze-hadees mein Mansoor bin Azan ney Muhammad bin Zuber ki mukhalifat ki hai.
3880,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insan us chiz mein nazar nahin maan sakta jis ka wo Malik nahin aur na Allah Taala ki nafarmani ki nazar maan sakta hai. Ali bin Zaid ney Mansoor bin Azan ki mukhalifat ki hai, us ney ye riwayat ba-wasta Hasan, Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan ki hai."
3881,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nafarmani ki nazar moatabar nahin aur na us chiz ki jis ka wo Malik nahin. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain Ali bin Zaid zaeef raawi hai. aur (us ki bayan karda) ye hadees khata hai, jabkey durust  (Abdur-Rehman bin Samura key bajaey) Imran bin Husain hi hai, isi ke sath Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye riwayat eik aur sanad sey bhi bayan ki gaee hai."
3882,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nafarmani ki nazar puri na ki jaey aur na us chiz ki jis ka wo insan Malik nahin.
3883,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko dekha jisey do shakhson key saharey chalaya ja raha tha. aap ney farmaya : aisey kyon? logon ney kaha : huzur ! us ney nazar maana hai ke Baitullah tak chal kar jaeyga. farmaya : Allah Taala ko kya zarurat ke ye shakhs apney aap ko azab mein daley? usey kaho sawar ho jaey."
3884,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik buzurg aadmi key paas sey guzrey jisey do aadmi sahara dey kar chala rahey they. farmaya : usey kya huwa? logon ney kaha is ney pedal chalney ki nazar maana hai. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ko koi zarurat nahin ke ye apney aap ko azab mein daley. usey kaho sawar ho jaey. to Mukhatib ney usey sawar honey ko kaha."
3885,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka guzar aisey shakhs par sey huwa jisey uskey do betey pakad kar saharey sey chala rahey they. aap ney farmaya : isey kya huwa? kaha gaya is ney Kaba tak pedal chalney ki nazar maana hai. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ko koi faeyda nahin ke ye apney aap ko azab mein daley. chunanche aap ney usey sawar honey ka hukm diya.
3886,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney qism khatey waqt Insha-Allah kaha, wo qism puri karney sey mustashnaa hogaya."
3887,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfooan (Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) se sidhey taur par) riwayat hai ke Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) alehissalam ney farmaya : main raat ko nawwey biwiyon key paas zarur jaaunga. un mein sey har eik aurat aisa ladka janeygi jo Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad kerega. aap sey kaha gaya : Insha-Allah kahin lekin unhoney na kaha, chunanche aap un sab key paas gaey lekin sirf eik aurat ney bachcha jana, wo bhi naqis. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar wo Insha-Allah keh detey to un ki qism na toot'ti aur un ki dili murad puri hoti."
